id_table_1.caption: TABLE I:  Evaluation of the proposed A3GC-IP model compared to DIP, Transpose and G-GRU on DIP-IMU [12] and Total Capture [56]. For DIP we list the result of the method as proposed by the authors as well as a version adopting global target rotations. We report the mean global angular error over the shoulder and hip joints (DIP Err), as well as the mean global angular error, the mean position error and the mean jerk error averaged over all 15 joints.
